Package: geotax
Type: Package
Title: Tools for exploring taxonomic distance over the geographical space
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: 
    person("Angel", "Robles", , "a.l.robles.fernandez@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-4674-4270"))
Description: This is a set of tools to model the probability that two potential
    host (or other classes of interactions) share a pathogen given a phylogenetic 
    or taxonomical distance.
